&lt;p>Below are described the main concepts of KRE.&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="krt">KRT&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>Konstellation Runtime Transport is a compressed file with the definition of a runtime version, included the code to
run and a YAML file called &lt;code>kre.yml&lt;/code> with the desired workflows definitions.&lt;/p>
